Movies@ Emnotweni is the place to watch any movie. From their comfortable seats to their clean theatres, it is a pleasurable experience for the whole family. But wait they did not stop there, they now have a scholars’ offer which entitles under 18s to a movie ticket, soda and popcorn for only R70! Having spent most of her life exploring the jungle with her parents, nothing could prepare Dora for her most terrifying adventure ever—high school. Always the explorer, Dora quickly finds herself leading Boots (her best friend, a monkey), Diego, a mysterious jungle inhabitant, and a ragtag group of teens on an adventure to save her parents (Eva Longoria and Michael Pea) and solve the impossible mystery behind a lost city of gold. Based on Dora the Explorer (TV series) by Valeri Walsh and Eric Weiner.      